有，如果是寄給熟悉的客戶或內部團隊，可以寫得比較輕鬆自然：

Hi HK Team,

The development is now completed and ready for your review.

Please find the attached test case and the generated CV Red Flag Report. Could you help take a look and confirm whether the output meets your expectations?

If anything needs to be adjusted, just let us know. Otherwise, a quick confirmation by reply would be greatly appreciated.

Thanks!

Best regards,

如果想再更口語一點：

We’ve finished the development on our side and it’s ready for review.

或

We’ve completed this phase and would like to get your feedback on the report output.

這兩句都很常見，聽起來比 “The development is now completed” 更自然一些。